{"id": 2563, "genre": 1000, "title": "工作之后，你都被迫接受了哪些特殊的交流规则？", "description": "那些感觉上有点作但又不得不用的办公室说话方式。（题图来自：iStock ©️ lankogal）", "record_count": 14425, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018101518322870qyQvbkSwdCfLXE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-15T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4790, "title": "工作之后，你都被迫接受了哪些特殊的交流规则？", "content": "工作之后，你都被迫接受了哪些特殊的交流规则？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 304187, "content": "不管大会小会，开会一定要抓个笔记本带上", "image": "img/option/option/20181015173445lHDhvKP0Zr3IQ9zu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304188, "content": "跟上级说话的时候一般以“好的”“收到”结尾", "image": "img/option/option/20181015172513svi6UCT23bPQad7u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304193, "content": "PPT 里加上一堆看不懂的图表和数据，会显得比较高端", "image": "img/option/option/201810151724361dseEI7SGCXMzOhJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304200, "content": "聊天时用各种行话、“黑话”，会显得自己很懂", "image": "img/option/option/20181015172243Cn7p5PrjtsoJS4RF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304201, "content": "发工作邮件时，按照职级填收件人和抄送人的邮箱地址", "image": "img/option/option/201810151712483IByKYj8zFLhMtpg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304203, "content": "邮件开头先写“如之前线下沟通”，表示自己一直在盯着", "image": "img/option/option/20181015172144NoTHlSEuCzUKG2Av.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304204, "content": "在群里发指令只能是上司@下属，反过来就不可以", "image": "img/option/option/201810151721338iwXxOjQq1nILVPK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 304206, "content": "口头/微信沟通不算数，一定要发邮件（领导派活除外）", "image": "img/option/option/20181015172115P1It8ebwacJMW9hj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}